Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel cold! I'm gonna become an oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what my Plague Rounds can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If he creates a virus and makes people suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save everyone at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! How dare you attack me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you attack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for killing Pay-Pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- But he's alive!\N- But he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight for the Kozuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The way they grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be an outdated concept...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But death brings humans completion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be so arrogant, Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting killed by you is not honorable for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Zoro's Pursuit! Ice Oni Tag!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awful! He even shot his allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do say so myself, this is a great show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Yo! Yo! Yo! Yo! Yo!\NYo! Yo! Yo! Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a deer in the headlights
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the hard bite will change you into an oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need tears! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't care about tomorrow! Make some noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Boss Hyogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than hurting my comrades, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jump the gun, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be an oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there is a cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Ohmasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sacrifice yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Hyogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the slightest idea of\Nwhat kind of disease this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but remember what happened in Udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't spread the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll cure you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that pestilence get the better of you!\NDon't lose hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When there's nothing we can do,\NI'll stop you by cutting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't do it! We're on the same side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen-sama, why did you shoot us, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold! It's cold! I'm becoming an oni...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...we still need more groove!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance! Shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go crazier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna turn into an oni! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch some excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the right person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's feature him and finish it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to keep them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they zombies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! More and more people are getting infected!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you can do, Chopper-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could cure them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's not realistically possible\Nto concoct a medicine while fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and give those oni shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike Udon,\Nwe have the guy who made the virus here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the virus creator made the antibody\Nat the same time and kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can get hold of it,\NI'll be able to make tons of medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all people, he's a Lead Performer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to grab that from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than their violent behavior,\NI'm more worried about what'll happen to them later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They gained ferocity and physical strength,\Nand their skin was rapidly cooled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bodies can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if we let the infected be, they'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they get infected,\Nthey'll only have an hour at most!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who turned into Ice Oni\Nwas your best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boss? Your subordinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be the most energetic moment of their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them a good hug for the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get infected though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That vermin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Queen!\NHow could he make another hideous weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna stay on this floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Brother Apoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only antibody in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for Ice Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose it,\Nyour punishment will be a savage death...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,An antibody...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...against Ice Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's an antibody!\N- If we can get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- We gotta grab that!\N- What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen presents!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Game Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoom! Zoom! Zoom! Zoom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It finally begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing was up to chance, it wouldn't be called a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder! Betrayal! There's no rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,An hour from now, you'll meet your...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard! He thinks so lightly of people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Oni...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...Tag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa-whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Grab that from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't let them have it!\N- Our people will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let those samurai get well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab it from each other!\NKill one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get caught you win, Apoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Crimson Cat Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Canine Scourge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys will die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lives will be over\Nwithout accomplishing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a meaningless death...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,RIGHT-BRAIN TOWER INSIDE THE DOME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna fight for the Kozuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can outrun us carrying them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, our mission is complete\Nif we can kill that brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...fight for the Kozuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are,\Nbut if you're on our side...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna save you too, Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,20 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching Kozuki Oden's execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M HAPPY IF PEOPLE TALK ABOUT ME OVER A DRINK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M HAPPY IF PEOPLE TALK ABOUT ME OVER A DRINK\N...if people talk about me over a drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden wouldn't be oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,IF IT WASN'T BOILED\N...if it wasn't boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think worked hard,\Nso you can live in peace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama had always been protecting this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who's the silly lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your speech brought me to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Kozuki Oden's way of life brought me to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kozuki Clan has no place\Nin the New Onigashima Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,On that terrible day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran to Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why... are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:21:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All I could do was watch you\Nas you were about to be dropped by Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You identified yourself as my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also known as...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...can die for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the concentrated fire of the Tobi Roppo,\NNami and Usopp have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Those who rebel against Kaido won't be forgiven!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As Ulti-Mortar closes in on her,\NNami is worn-out both physically and mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In this dire circumstance,\Nthe promise that she made with Luffy comes to mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Nami Surrenders?! Ulti's Fierce Headbutt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
